document.full_text: missouri suffered a small earthquake tuesday that caused no deaths or injuries, a relatively minor blow for a state hit by a series of natural disasters this spring including tornadoes, floods, soaring temperatures, and even cicadas.
document.title: earthquake latest in natural disasters to hit missouri
